## CRITICAL: Always pass --repo

Every `gh` command MUST include `--repo {{FULL_NAME}}`:

```bash
gh pr create --repo {{FULL_NAME}} --base main --title "..."
gh pr list   --repo {{FULL_NAME}}
gh pr merge  --repo {{FULL_NAME}} <number> --merge
gh issue list --repo {{FULL_NAME}}
```

